title: 179: The Trader Joe's Pumpkin Haul (and More) Episode!
itunes:title: The Trader Joe's Pumpkin Haul (and More) Episode!
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa and the gang are taste-testing a ton of pumpkin stuff and other interesting fall finds from TJ’s. There’s pumpkin yogurt, pumpkin gnocchi, pumpkin spice granola bark, pumpkin waffles, pumpkin biscotti, pumpkin cream cheese, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, you don’t want to miss which find received an 11 out of 10 on Lisa’s scale. IT’S SO GOOD! Why haven’t you pressed play yet? And once you’re done listening to the episode, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the products we tried.
itunes:summary: Pumpkin season is here and we found some great (and some not so great) pumpkin finds at Trader Joe’s!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
dc:creator: Lisa Lillien
